      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs001-02.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 9.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、一人で自主練してたのか？",
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もうすぐライブバトルなので\n本番までに振り付けを完璧にしておきたくて……",
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "入所した頃は体力がなくてダンスも苦手だったのに\n千紗も成長したな",
      "startTime": 28.5433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、嬉しいです\n最近はダンスを重点的に練習してるんです",
      "startTime": 33.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "この間なんて怜ちゃんからも\nダンスがうまくなったって褒められたんですよ",
      "startTime": 40.51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんにはレッスン中によく叱られてたから\n私も成長してるんだって思えて嬉しかったなぁ……",
      "startTime": 48.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば以前、怜から相談を受けたことがあったな",
      "startTime": 53.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}